text: Antonie Stárová (born 12 October 1998) is a Czech footballer who plays as a midfielder for NC State WolfpackProfile at NC State Wolfpack websiteProfile at University of Delaware website and has appeared for the Czech Republic women's national team. ==Career== Stárová has been capped for the Czech Republic national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:People from Nymburk District Category:Czech women's footballers Category:Czech Republic women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:AC Sparta Praha (women) players Category:Expatriate women's soccer players in the United States Category:NC State Wolfpack women's soccer players Category:Czech expatriate sportspeople in the United States Category:Czech First Division (women) players
